<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= config.language %>">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - 页面未找到 | <%= config.title %></title>
  
  <!-- Styles -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%- url_for(theme.css) %>/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  
  <!-- Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="cyber-body">
  <!-- Glitch effect overlay -->
  <div class="glitch-overlay"></div>
  
  <!-- Main container -->
  <div class="cyber-container">
    <div class="error-page">
      <div class="error-content">
        <!-- 错误代码 -->
        <div class="error-code">
          <span class="digit">4</span>
          <span class="digit glitch-digit">0</span>
          <span class="digit">4</span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 错误标题 -->
        <h1 class="error-title">页面未找到</h1>
        
        <!-- 错误描述 -->
        <div class="error-description">
          <p>看起来你访问的页面已经消失在数字空间中。</p>
          <p>可能是链接错误、页面已被移除，或者它从未存在过。</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 错误详情 -->
        <div class="error-details">
          <div class="error-info">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
            <span>错误代码: 404_NOT_FOUND</span>
          </div>
          <div class="error-info">
            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            <span>时间: <span id="current-time"></span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="error-info">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
            <span>位置: 数字空间未知区域</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 操作按钮 -->
        <div class="error-actions">
          <a href="<%- url_for('/') %>" class="error-btn primary">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            返回首页
          </a>
          <a href="<%- url_for('/archives') %>" class="error-btn secondary">
            <i class="fas fa-archive"></i>
            浏览归档
          </a>
          <button onclick="history.back()" class="error-btn accent">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
            返回上一页
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 搜索框 -->
        <div class="error-search">
          <p>或者搜索你想要的内容：</p>
          <form class="search-form" action="/search" method="get">
            <input type="text" name="q" class="search-input" placeholder="输入关键词搜索...">
            <button type="submit" class="search-button">
              <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 趣味提示 -->
        <div class="error-hint">
          <div class="hint-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="hint-content">
            <h4>赛博空间小贴士</h4>
            <p>在数字世界中，404错误就像赛博朋克城市中的暗巷——它们存在，但最好避免进入。如果你经常遇到这种情况，可能是时候检查你的神经链接了。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 页脚 -->
      <footer class="error-footer">
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="<%- url_for('/about') %>">关于</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/1jinbo/Vision" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
          <a href="/archives">归档</a>
          <a href="/tags">标签</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-copyright">
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= config.author || config.title %> | Cyber Minimal Theme
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Scripts -->
  <script>
    // 更新时间显示
    function updateTime() {
      const now = new Date();
      const timeStr = now.toLocaleString('zh-CN', {
        year: 'numeric',
        month: '2-digit',
        day: '2-digit',
        hour: '2-digit',
        minute: '2-digit',
        second: '2-digit',
        hour12: false
      });
      document.getElementById('current-time').textContent = timeStr;
    }
    
    // 初始更新
    updateTime();
    
    // 每秒更新
    setInterval(updateTime, 1000);
    
    // Glitch效果
    const glitchDigit = document.querySelector('.glitch-digit');
    setInterval(() => {
      glitchDigit.style.textShadow = `
        ${Math.random() * 4 - 2}px ${Math.random() * 4 - 2}px 0 #00ff9d,
        ${Math.random() * 4 - 2}px ${Math.random() * 4 - 2}px 0 #ff00ff
      `;
      glitchDigit.style.color = Math.random() > 0.5 ? '#00ff9d' : '#ff00ff';
    }, 100);
    
    // 鼠标移动效果
    document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
      const x = e.clientX / window.innerWidth;
      const y = e.clientY / window.innerHeight;
      
      document.querySelector('.error-content').style.transform = 
        `translate(${x * 10 - 5}px, ${y * 10 - 5}px)`;
    });
  </script>
  
  <style>
    .error-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .error-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.1s ease;
    }
    
    .error-code {
      font-size: 8rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    
    .digit {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--primary);
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.5),
        0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .glitch-digit {
      animation: glitch 0.5s infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes glitch {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      20% { transform: translate(-2px, 2px); }
      40% { transform: translate(2px, -1px); }
      60% { transform: translate(-1px, 1px); }
      80% { transform: translate(1px, -2px); }
    }
    
    .error-title {
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .error-description {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .error-details {
      background: var(--bg-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .error-info {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    
    .error-info:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .error-info i {
      color: var(--secondary);
      width: 20px;
    }
    
    .error-actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .error-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border: 2px solid;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    .error-btn.primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      border-color: var(--primary);
      color: var(--bg-dark);
    }
    
    .error-btn.primary:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.3);
    }
    
    .error-btn.secondary {
      background: transparent;
      border-color: var(--secondary);
      color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    .error-btn.secondary:hover {
      background: var(--secondary);
      color: var(--bg-dark);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.3);
    }
    
    .error-btn.accent {
      background: transparent;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .error-btn.accent:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg-dark);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.3);
    }
    
    .error-search {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .error-search p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .error-search .search-form {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .error-hint {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .hint-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    
    .hint-content h4 {
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .hint-content p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .error-footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .footer-links a {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .footer-links a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    
    .footer-copyright {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .error-code {
        font-size: 5rem;
      }
      
      .error-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .error-description {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      
      .error-btn {
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      
      .error-hint {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>